pating families can earn up to 350 from the individual 25 reimbursement for each visit and a completed questionnaire packet  anyone interested in learning more or participating can call 765 494 6610 or email ajlab purdue edu this study is funded by a 900 000 grant that schwichtenberg received in 2011 from the national institute of mental health  '
